      "overview_item_title": "Essential Ideas",
      "overview_item_data": {
        "overview_item_data_type": "list",
        "overview_item_data_items": [
          "You can make sense of integer addition using a real-world situation.",
          "You can write an equation to represent a situation with integers.",
          "When combining numbers modeled by opposite directions, the sign of the resulting location corresponds to the sign of the cube showing the greater distance.",
          "When combining numbers representing the same direction, the resulting direction is the same as the original direction."
